Our e-waste management practices, in partnership with Ecologic in France for certified WEEE recycling, ensure responsible disposal of electronic waste, further supporting sustainable development goals. By providing carbon reporting aligned with GRI Standards (though partially), we can monitor and report on the carbon footprint of our solutions effectively, contributing to transparency and continuous improvement.

Additionally, our typical energy reduction practices achieve a 35% reduction in energy consumption compared to baseline scenarios, which can be tailored to meet the specific needs of the City of Belval's project. By implementing these sustainable solutions, we can significantly reduce the environmental footprint of the information systems while supporting the city's policy of sustainable development and contributing to its goals of minimizing energy consumption and relying on low-carbon infrastructure.
